# Rust Service

Rust service managed by codefly.

## Structure

- `code/Cargo.toml` -- crate manifest
- `code/src/main.rs` -- entrypoint (axum HTTP server on the port assigned by codefly)

## Commands

- Build: `cargo build`
- Test: `cargo test`
- Run: run the binary from `code/`

The service resolves its listen address through the `codefly-sdk` crate
injected by the codefly runtime.
